GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 12th November, 2019:
i)
Shri Arvind Ganpat Sawant relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Heavy
Industries and Public Enterprises;
Shri Prakash Javadekar assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of Heavy
Industries and Public Enterprises. He will continue to hold the charge of the office of the
Minister of Environment, Forest and Climate Change; and the office of the Minister of
Information and Broadcasting.
Copy forwarded for information to:
Secretary to the President.
Secretary to the Vice-President.
MOST IMMEDIATE
New Delhi, the 12th November, 2019
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to the Vice-Chairperson, NITI Aayog.
Copy also forwarded for information to :
Principal Secretary to the Prime Minister.
Principal Adviser to the Prime Minister.
*JK*
400 Copies.
